# Day 25 – AI Shark Tank Simulator

## Project Overview
Built a fully functional AI Shark Tank Simulator as a single HTML application using Claude AI.

## Features
- Startup Pitch Form
- 4 AI Shark Judges
- Interactive Pitch Round
- AI-Based Startup Scoring
- Investment Decision
- Valuation & Funding Recommendation
- Leaderboard
- Download Pitch Report
- Share Result
- Responsive Dark UI

## Technologies Used
- HTML5
- CSS3
- JavaScript

## Learning Outcomes
- Built an interactive AI-inspired web application.
- Improved frontend development skills.
- Learned UI/UX design for startup simulation.
- Practiced prompt engineering with Claude AI.

